title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Smoke Lamar in the New Hunting Pack Remix
content:
Lamar Davis is in big trouble again. In this new take on Hunting Pack, the LD Organics van is on fire — clouding Lamar’s mind and vision — while a rival gang is in hot pursuit.

Play Hunting Pack (Get Lamar) through April 23 to earn 2X GTA$ and RP, doubling to 4X Rewards for GTA+ Members. Winning two rounds of Hunting Pack (Get Lamar) will also complete the Weekly Challenge and get you the Black High Brass Tee in addition to GTA$100,000.
